The paper deals with data management systems and algorithmic solutions for complex query answering over distributed, high-dimensional data streams in the sliding-window model. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the database (cs.DB), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), social and information networks (cs.SI), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
